commit message: Fixed problem where obfuscation would cause ACRA to throw exception on launch. Heavy handedly I disabled all obfuscation

Fixed problem where with locale using a , for decimal point seperator,
wrote gpx file in incorrect format

Fixed long standing bug with SeekBar

Now has password timeout option

'Back to main' in Settings changed to 'Go to main' and goes to the main
screen no matter what

Fixed problem where if phone is using certain languages (such as
German), GPX output file uses commas rather than dots for decimal
separator
